net.rim.device.api.collection
Interface LongKeyProviderAdaptor

public interface LongKeyProviderAdaptor

Adaptor class that can retrieve long integer keys for collections that can use them.

LongSortedReadableList collections can make use of objects impelmenting this interface to extract the long integer keys it requires from its contained elements.

Whether this key is actually contained in the element object, or whether it is generated by the adaptor itself based on other data contained in the element, is up to the implementor.
